gorgeous). It's also very important to consider the size of your space; larger home theaters won't be served well by a system with satellites instead of floor speakers, and putting the JBL Synthesis Everest in a master bedroom is going to yield incredibly disappointing results, unless you just want to blow your windows out! Be sure to consider all of these elements when making your purchase to ensure that you are satisfied with the money you spend, but above all, remember to enjoy your new system!For more information on what to look at in selecting the best home theater speakers in 2022, We have listed below the best home theater speaker available for you to help you decide what product is best to buy.</div>
        

        
